                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9072" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0266</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1554 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“碳”索顺丰，“零”跑未来——ESG的物流发展创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Explore SF Express and lead the future——ESG&#39;s logistics development and innovation road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">闵继胜，刘康，胡天赐，孙雨，胡雪梅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顺丰控股股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">物流行业；ESG；低碳发展；创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Logistics industry; ESG; Low-carbon development;Innovate</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述的是顺丰控股低碳发展取得极大进展的具体碳管理措施。该企业所属物流行业2023年碳排放占全国碳排放总量的9%左右，温室气体排放量显著，急需构建现代物流体系助力行业低碳发展。在国家提出“双碳”目标之前顺丰就已经开始布局节能降碳，低碳发展之下，企业价值也发展迅速，2022年和2023年是唯一进入世界500强的中国民营快递企业，也是唯一一家物流公司荣登“中国ESG影响力榜”。本案例以顺丰控股ESG发展战略为主线，通过采取ESG战略，初步形成以数字科技底盘、全面绿色运行、智慧供应链技术、碳捕捉技术、风险管理体系等围绕“E”领域的创新举措推进企业低碳发展，“零”碳发展取得了阶段性成果，帮助公司价值实现巨大提升。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes specific carbon management measures that SF Holding has made great progress in low-carbon development. The company&#39;s logistics industry in 2023 carbon emissions accounted for about 9% of the country&#39;s total carbon emissions, greenhouse gas emissions are significant, there is an urgent need to build a modern logistics system to help the low-carbon development of the industry. Before the country put forward the &quot;double carbon&quot; goal, SF Express has begun to layout energy saving and carbon reduction, under the low-carbon development, the enterprise value is also developing rapidly, 2022 and 2023 is the only Chinese private express enterprises to enter the world&#39;s top 500, but also the only logistics company won the &quot;China ESG Influence List&quot;. This case takes the ESG development strategy of SF Holding as the main line. By adopting ESG strategy, the company has initially formed innovative measures in the field of &quot;E&quot;, such as digital technology chassis, comprehensive green operation, smart supply chain technology, carbon capture technology, and risk management system to promote the low-carbon development of the company. The &quot;zero&quot; carbon development has achieved stage results and helped the company achieve a great increase in value.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论；可持续发展理论；风险管理理论；战略性社会责任理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
